{"tid":450482,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★林奮強 : 綠置居? 擁有業權不用「除名」一家人住在一起，只是擠迫一點","createTime":"2017-10-28T08:37:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-28T12:58:38.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"0df041d9089cdafb20ac3a3f02378ef1d26d600e","tid":450482,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T08:37:42.000Z","msg":"若公屋戶能擁有單位業權，他們便能像私樓業主般「最優化」（optimise）其單位的使用：<br />\n<br />\n公屋富戶再不用「分戶」或「除名」，<span style=\"color: red;\">即使子女出身亦不用搬離家中，甚至加入輪候冊，等於從源頭減少公屋需求，一家人能繼續住在一起。這當然會擠迫一點，</span>但在私人單位，這情況已發生 10 年。而公/私單位的個人空間（人均居住面積）相差無幾，公屋住迫一點也不為過。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對於年屆退休之齡的公屋戶主而言，若他們的公屋單位能在市場出售，正如莊太量教授在團結香港基金的論壇上指，隨着跨境交通日漸便捷，公屋業主便多了一個自由選擇，可以沽出單位（尤其是若該單位位於市區），回鄉養老。如此一來，騰空的便不止是一個房間，而是一整個單位。<br />\n<br />\n換言之，出售公屋除了可以控制公屋需求的增長，還可以增加市場上出租（甚至出售）單位（或房間）的供應，幫助紓緩房屋問題。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/blogger/296/avatar/f1e216311d328b87c18ba619d140dba1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fblogger%2F296%2Favatar%2Ff1e216311d328b87c18ba619d140dba1.jpg&h=d5eb9328&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/01博評-政經社/128936/-房屋政策-博評-經土地注入財富-出售公屋將扭轉資產不均\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F01%E5%8D%9A%E8%A9%95-%E6%94%BF%E7%B6%93%E7%A4%BE%2F128936%2F-%E6%88%BF%E5%B1%8B%E6%94%BF%E7%AD%96-%E5%8D%9A%E8%A9%95-%E7%B6%93%E5%9C%9F%E5%9C%B0%E6%B3%A8%E5%85%A5%E8%B2%A1%E5%AF%8C-%E5%87%BA%E5%94%AE%E5%85%AC%E5%B1%8B%E5%B0%87%E6%89%AD%E8%BD%89%E8%B3%87%E7%94%A2%E4%B8%8D%E5%9D%87&d=0P7X5MaZ0MklmEu5q2zIJU%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=000bc3fc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/01博評-政經社/128936/-房屋政策-博評-經土地注入財富-出售公屋將扭轉資產不均</a>"},{"pid":"1c1c06f06eaa85701a3b161886def5e513e598aa","tid":450482,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T08:38:18.000Z","msg":"會擠迫一點<br />\n會擠迫一點<br />\n會擠迫一點<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aa4cb44af5bd08d1e9d82f6d42d6e7053cb250d","tid":450482,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T08:42:19.000Z","msg":"屌你老母係咪要人四代同堂住一個250呎單位？"},{"pid":"18a8a10ba13b251ff8bca28e08df70646c948901","tid":450482,"uid":23141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T08:43:11.000Z","msg":"解決提出問題嘅人，幾時都係最方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51e31c63e0e3d6c094aab56bf4de379f0ff49e3f","tid":450482,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T08:44:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會擠迫一點<br />\n會擠迫一點<br />\n會擠迫一點<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係扑嘢都冇地方"},{"pid":"34f5f70e0af93aa417f0aa85eef8a6cc950647d9","tid":450482,"uid":46332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T08:44:54.000Z","msg":"不如你自己帶頭先?"},{"pid":"e3ef0f251e70fa2ec311cd9105af84a40160d305","tid":450482,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T08:45:17.000Z","msg":"好過訓金拱門"},{"pid":"8ec5e9c29196755cec6b1a1ade222284b7caafe5","tid":450482,"uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T08:46:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你老母係咪要人四代同堂住一個250呎單位？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nlike this<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/28/164641_38e2b0c9910417f56c2a5b72fa2287d4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F28%2F164641_38e2b0c9910417f56c2a5b72fa2287d4.jpg&h=1f23c0cd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fbc19982ea0e868c116c0c59c2a0ea0cd4ae0322","tid":450482,"uid":74012,"like":3,"