if\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d43a73687a3b41b2a59b7cd9e63c57cb976bc692","tid":450482,"uid":52595,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T12:52:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9e39eeaa05d056318b2cf9116bafff8f59749cbe","tid":450482,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T12:57:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解要叫我地回鄉養老??<br />\n<br />\n自問唔激進反中, 但我對中國大陸冇感情, 點解要我呢種陀地港燦上去住, 但比班蝗黎住我成長的地方???</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n重有，好多人三代都是香港人( me too ) ，回咩鄉？<br />\n邊度鄉？<br />\n雖然身份証以前是要填藉冠！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n回鄉？伊甸園?"},{"pid":"6c3c562f9fb10a53e908caf28603b78fcfbc577c","tid":450482,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T12:58:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>解決提出問題嘅人，幾時都係最方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這一直是共產黨解決問題的最佳方案！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n把提出問題的人解決了，那就沒有問題啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}